name: Kurzgesagt-ArtStyle LoRA
description:
Kurzgesagt Style LoRA, you can use SD artist to enhance quality.

Use tags like: civilization, people, city, sci-fi, bird, alien planet, astronaut

This is a LoRA model, you will need new version Automatic's 1111 SD-WebUI or additional-networks extension

modelVersions.name: v1-DreamLike
modelVersions.description:
Base on Dreamlike Diffusion model

Stop at CLIP layers=1

meta.prompt:
